WEBVTT

00:02.130 --> 00:04.099
So, what exactly is this?

00:08.962 --> 00:13.008
If you want a camera, it becomes a digital camera.

00:13.843 --> 00:15.784
Easily held in one hand.

00:19.884 --> 00:25.956
If you want a music player, it becomes a B&O premium hi-fi music player.

00:31.409 --> 00:34.943
You can take shots as wide as your own eyes can see.

00:37.619 --> 00:41.723
And check the time, always there without even lifting a finger.

00:43.982 --> 00:48.800
But this thing that lets you easily take charge, have fun, and play...

00:48.959 --> 00:50.555
...with all these new devices.

00:51.529 --> 00:52.731
So, what is this?

00:53.434 --> 00:55.773
LG G5 and friends.

00:56.725 --> 00:59.122
Life's good when you play more.

00:59.701 --> 01:01.243
LG G5.

